#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:12
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Discover the features Portage has, such as support for distributed compiling,\n"
"ccache and more.\n"
msgstr "Portageの持つ、分散コンパイルやccacheのサポートなど、より多くの機能を知ってください。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:20
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Portage Features"
msgstr "Portageの機能"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:24
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Portage has several additional features that makes your Gentoo experience even\n"
"better. Many of these features rely on certain software tools that improve\n"
"performance, reliability, security, ...\n"
msgstr ""
"PortageはあなたのGentoo環境をより良くしてくれるいくつかの追加の機能があります。\n"
"これらの機能の多くはパフォーマンス、信頼性、セキュリティなどを改良してくれるソフトウェアツールに頼っています。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:30
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To enable or disable certain Portage features you need to edit\n"
"<path>/etc/make.conf</path>'s <c>FEATURES</c> variable which contains the\n"
"various feature keywords, separated by white space. In several cases you\n"
"will also need to install the additional tool on which the feature relies.\n"
msgstr ""
"Portageの機能を有効にしたり無効にするには、スペースで区切られた様々な機能のキーワードを含む<path>/etc/make.conf</path>の<c>FEATURES</c>変数を編集する必要があります。\n"
"いくつかのケースでは機能が依存している追加のツールをインストールする必要があります。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:37
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Not all features that Portage supports are listed here. For a full overview,\n"
"please consult the <path>make.conf</path> man page:\n"
msgstr ""
"Portageがサポートしている機能が全てここで紹介されているわけではありません。\n"
"全てを知るには、<path>make.conf</path>のmanページを調べてください。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:41
