#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-working-features.xml:188
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To check if ccache functions, ask ccache to provide you with its statistics.\n"
"Because Portage uses a different ccache home directory, you need to set the\n"
"<c>CCACHE_DIR</c> variable as well:\n"
